{
  "id": "5c8f1c73806a2c0017ec0114",
  "title": "濱口秀司のコラボレーション実験",
  "created": 1552882807,
  "updated": 1590141385,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5c8f1c73806a2c0017ec0114",
      "text": "濱口秀司のコラボレーション実験",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1552882807,
      "updated": 1552882811
    },
    {
      "id": "5c8f1c7baff09e00007d8ef3",
      "text": "[濱口 秀司]の[コラボレーション]実験",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1552882811,
      "updated": 1552882822
    },
    {
      "id": "5c8f1c85aff09e00007d8ef5",
      "text": "一人で考えるのと大勢で考えるのの比較実験",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1552882822,
      "updated": 1552882911
    },
    {
      "id": "5c8f1cdfaff09e00007d8ef9",
      "text": "\tA: 1時間議論",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1552882911,
      "updated": 1552882998
    },
    {
      "id": "5c8f1ce2aff09e00007d8efa",
      "text": "\tB: 20分間黙って一人で考えて、残りの40分で議論",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1552882915,
      "updated": 1552883001
    },
    {
      "id": "5c8f1cf4aff09e00007d8efb",
      "text": "\tC: 20分間黙って一人で考えて、共有してからもう20分黙って考えて、最後の20分で議論",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1552882932,
      "updated": 1552883003
    },
    {
      "id": "5c8f1d04aff09e00007d8efc",
      "text": "\tD: 40分間黙って一人で考えて、最後の20分で議論",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1552882949,
      "updated": 1552883005
    },
    {
      "id": "5c8f1d19aff09e00007d8efe",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1552882969,
      "updated": 1552882969
    },
    {
      "id": "5c8f1d3eaff09e00007d8eff",
      "text": "Aが悪く、B, C, DはAより良くて、中でもCがもっとも良い",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1552883007,
      "updated": 1552883036
    },
    {
      "id": "5c8f1cc4aff09e00007d8ef8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1552882885,
      "updated": 1552882885
    },
    {
      "id": "5c8f1d76aff09e00007d8f00",
      "text": "[4 濱口秀司さんのアイデアのカケラたち。 - ほぼ日刊イトイ新聞 https://www.1101.com/hamaguchihideshi/2017-11-27.html#main]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1552883062,
      "updated": 1552883072
    },
    {
      "id": "5c8f1d80aff09e00007d8f01",
      "text": "実験の詳しい話はどこで読めるのかな？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1552883073,
      "updated": 1552883112
    },
    {
      "id": "5c8f1d88aff09e00007d8f02",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1552883080,
      "updated": 1552883080
    },
    {
      "id": "5c8f1ca6aff09e00007d8ef7",
      "text": "関連",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1552882854,
      "updated": 1552883281
    },
    {
      "id": "5c8f1e90aff09e0000456466",
      "text": "\t[まず自分で書く]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1552883345,
      "updated": 1552883345
    },
    {
      "id": "5c8f1e50aff09e000094513a",
      "text": "\t[共創の前にまず独創]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1552883281,
      "updated": 1552883285
    },
    {
      "id": "5c8f1e50aff09e0000945139",
      "text": "\t[一人でやるかみんなでやるか]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1552883281,
      "updated": 1552883297
    },
    {
      "id": "5c8f1e5baff09e000094513b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1552883292,
      "updated": 1552883292
    },
    {
      "id": "5caab311aff09e0000843647",
      "text": "http://www.dhbr.net/articles/-/5008",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554690833,
      "updated": 1554690858
    },
    {
      "id": "5caab32baff09e0000843649",
      "text": "ハーバードビジネスレビュー 2017 10月号 p.120",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554690860,
      "updated": 1554691368
    },
    {
      "id": "5caab528aff09e000084364a",
      "text": "\t202個入りの積み木(kuum)の2セットが与えられ、60分で「すごい作品を作れ」という課題",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554691368,
      "updated": 1554691426
    },
    {
      "id": "5caab559aff09e000084364b",
      "text": "\tすごさの定義や評価基準はチームに委ねられる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554691418,
      "updated": 1554691469
    },
    {
      "id": "5caab58caff09e000084364c",
      "text": "\tこの実験は3チームに別れている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554691469,
      "updated": 1554691493
    },
    {
      "id": "5caab5a4aff09e000084364d",
      "text": "\t\tA: メンバーの自由に任せる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554691493,
      "updated": 1554691501
    },
    {
      "id": "5caab5acaff09e000084364e",
      "text": "\t\tB: 40分個々人で作品を作り、その後シェア",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554691501,
      "updated": 1554691515
    },
    {
      "id": "5caab5baaff09e000084364f",
      "text": "\t\tC: 20分個々人で作品を作り、その後シェア、それからバイアスモデルを考え、バイアスをブレイクする",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554691515,
      "updated": 1554691546
    },
    {
      "id": "5caab32aaff09e0000843648",
      "text": "\t結果",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554690858,
      "updated": 1554691571
    },
    {
      "id": "5caab5f3aff09e0000843651",
      "text": "\t\tAチームは議論で時間を使いきり、作品完成に至らなかった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554691571,
      "updated": 1554691581
    },
    {
      "id": "5caab5fcaff09e0000843652",
      "text": "\t\tBチームは40分の間に興味深い発想に至った個人がいて、共有フェーズでその発想が採用された",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554691581,
      "updated": 1554691646
    },
    {
      "id": "5caab669aff09e0000843655",
      "text": "\t\t\t積み木を使ってパラパラマンガを作り始めた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554691689,
      "updated": 1554691699
    },
    {
      "id": "5caab62caff09e0000843653",
      "text": "\t\tCチームは20分の間に興味深い発想には至らなかった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554691628,
      "updated": 1554691655
    },
    {
      "id": "5caab647aff09e0000843654",
      "text": "\t\t\tしかし出てきた作品をみて議論をした結果、出てきた作品が「止まっていることを前提にしている」というバイアスを発見した",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554691655,
      "updated": 1554691761
    },
    {
      "id": "5caab6b1aff09e0000843656",
      "text": "\t\t\tそのバイアスをブレイクすることを考えた結果、動きのある作品が作られた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554691761,
      "updated": 1554691795
    },
    {
      "id": "5caab6d3aff09e0000843657",
      "text": "\t\tBチームとCチームが同点だった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554691795,
      "updated": 1554691810
    },
    {
      "id": "5caab5f0aff09e0000843650",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554691568,
      "updated": 1554691568
    },
    {
      "id": "5caab74caff09e0000843658",
      "text": "\t一人で考えて、具体的なものを作ってから切り口の議論をすることが有用",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554691917,
      "updated": 1554691934
    },
    {
      "id": "5caab75daff09e000084365a",
      "text": "\t\t具体的アイデアと抽象的切り口のペアであることが重要",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554691934,
      "updated": 1554691948
    },
    {
      "id": "5ec7a19aaff09e000053f49a",
      "text": "\t\t[具体と抽象の結合が重要]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1590141338,
      "updated": 1590141364
    },
    {
      "id": "5caab76caff09e000084365b",
      "text": " \t最初から議論を始めたAチームは抽象的切り口の議論に終始した",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554691948,
      "updated": 1590141385
    },
    {
      "id": "5caab792aff09e000084365c",
      "text": "\t >[コラボレーションの要諦は議論しないこと]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554691987,
      "updated": 1554691995
    },
    {
      "id": "5caab751aff09e0000843659",
      "text": "\t\t\tCチームは20分間バイアスについての議論をしたが、ここで7人それぞれがバイアスを考える並列作業をした方が良かったのではと濱口は考えている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554691922,
      "updated": 1554692131
    },
    {
      "id": "5caab823aff09e000084365f",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tこの考えに基づいて別のワークショップを行い、実際に良かった、とのこと",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554692131,
      "updated": 1554692145
    },
    {
      "id": "5caab830aff09e0000843660",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554692145,
      "updated": 1554692257
    },
    {
      "id": "5caab8a1aff09e0000843661",
      "text": "\t[コラボレーションの3つのポイント]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554692258,
      "updated": 1554692282
    },
    {
      "id": "5caab7bcaff09e000084365d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1554692029,
      "updated": 1554692029
    }
  ]
}